               <desc type="abstract" xml:lang="en" xml:id="abstract2932-1">The bay which separates the <placeName
                     ref="http://syriaca.org/place/716">Arabian Peninsula</placeName> from the <placeName>Horn
                  of <placeName>Africa</placeName></placeName>.</desc>
               <desc xml:lang="en">A gulf connecting to the <placeName>Red
                  Sea</placeName> in the west located between <placeName>Somalia</placeName>, the <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/716">Arabian Peninsula</placeName>, and the <placeName>Arabian
                  Sea</placeName>.</desc>
